        "subject": "LU-4533 lprocfs: Increase OBD_HIST_MAX to OSC_MAX_RIF_MAX",
        "message": "LU-4533 lprocfs: Increase OBD_HIST_MAX to OSC_MAX_RIF_MAX\n\nSet OBD_HIST_MAX to 256 to match OSC_MAX_RIF_MAX so that the rpcs in\nflight histogram which is diplayed by reading the rpc_stats proc\ninterface is correct.\n\nSigned-off-by: Ryan Haasken <haasken@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I6118bf258a76e7791071744f9862d018b732672e\n"
